## Audio Recording

- Format: M4A (AAC), 44100Hz, mono, 128kbps
- Saved to Documents/Recordings/ (not temp dir)
- AVAudioRecorderDelegate for error handling
- Audio level metering at 0.1s intervals
- iOS 17+ uses AVAudioApplication.requestRecordPermission()
- iOS 16 fallback uses AVAudioSession.requestRecordPermission()
- Bluetooth support (.allowBluetooth option)

